Class ConnectionData

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--net.sourceforge.gjtapi.ConnectionData
public class ConnectionData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This is a simple Connection data carrier used for call snapshot delivery from dynamic or throttled TelephonyProviders. This is contained within a CallData object that it connects to.

The state given should be of type Connction state public final variables. Creation date: (2000-06-15 14:05:44)
